{"title":"The 2021 Brother Cycles Big Bro Goes Boost and Receives a Yellow Paintjob","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/03/the-2021-brother-cycles-big-bro-goes-boost-and-receives-a-yellow-paintjob/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-2021-brother-cycles-big-bro-goes-boost-and-receives-a-yellow-paintjob","date":1614765907000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-24.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206563\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-24.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-24.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-24.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-24.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-24.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-24.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-24.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" /></p>\n<p>Brother Cycles&#8217; Big Bro rigid mountain bike is a favorite among trail riders as well as bikepackers and for 2021, it got a bit of a refresh. The obvious change is this new yellow paint job, while the drivetrain has gone boost-spacing. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-37.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone siz