uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-41.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" /></p>\n<p>Now the Big Bro comes in 12x148mm rear spacing and 15x110mm front. The rest of the specs remain the same as the 2020 model. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-27.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206562\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-27.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-27.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-27.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-27.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-27.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-27.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-27.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-28.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206561\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-28.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/BrotherCycles-BigBro-2021-PerryWoods-28.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/202